subject: Basketball (College)
Series
NCAA Basketball Championships (Women)
lead_paragraph: The Florida Gulf Coast University women’s basketball team, which is averaging 9.6 made 3-point attempts a game, is 27-2 — 209-45 since joining Division I in 2007.
